==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-eɪt|-eɪt]]

===Verb===
{{en-verb|inflat|ing}}

# {{transitive}} [[enlarge|Enlarging]] an object by [[push]]ing air (or a gas) into it. 
#:''You '''inflate''' a balloon by blowing air into it.''
# {{intransitive}} To [[enlarge]] by [[fill]]ing with air (or a gas) into it. 
#:''The balloon will '''inflate''' if you blow into it.''

